[Only including dataset "Train"] Squares are categorical associations (uncertainty coefficient & correlation ratio) from 0 to 1. Circles are the symmetrical numerical correlations (Pearson's) from -1 to 1. The trivial diagonal is intentionally left blank for clarity.
